# Mappers Style

- Keep mapper interfaces small and explicit (`fromXDto`, `toXDto`).
- Implement mappers in `mappers/impl` using `ModelMapper`.
- Annotate mapper implementations with `@Component`.
- Prefer 1:1 field naming between DTOs and entities to keep mapping simple.
- Avoid business rules in mappers; use them only for shape conversion.
